Our expectation when we end up looking at payments revenues kind of overall across the categories that by the time we get to -- by the end of the fourth quarter, or certainly is very early in the 2022 sort of time frame that we will be back to pre-pandemic levels on a total basis, in terms of total merchant acquiring total credit, debit card as well as the CPS businesses.

David Rochester -- Compass Point -- Analyst

