Mark, what would you add?

Mark G. Runkel -- Senior Executive Vice President and Chief Credit Officer

Yeah, that's exactly spot on. There's not much more to add. We're just thinking over time, we'll get back to a more normalized level on those fee -- some of those recoveries that you're seeing potentially come down and then we'll see the portfolio start to normalize back closer to that 50 basis point range.

Betsy Graseck -- Morgan Stanley -- Analyst

